name: EPSColorSpace

properties.name: RGB
properties.description: Represents all color values using the RGB color space. Best suited for documents that will be viewed on-screen.

properties.name: CMYK
properties.description: Creates a separable file by representing all color values using the gamut of CYMK process color inks.

properties.name: GRAY
properties.description: Converts all color values to high-quality black-and-white images. Gray levels of the converted objects represent the luminosity of the original objects.

properties.name: UNCHANGED_COLOR_SPACE
properties.description: Leaves each image in its original color space.

description: Color space options for representing color in the exported EPS.
